5. Integration with the Rapacke Portal
In your Rapacke Portal, you should list this MIT-licensed repository as "Public Infrastructure," while keeping your "Provisional Patent" documents in the "Encrypted Vault" section. This creates a clear boundary between your Open Innovation (the community tools) and your Sovereign IP (the core math).

